      <div xml:id="Aink5-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> ituvumatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink5">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
          <l> paciyil lākuka piṇicē ṇīṅkuka</l>
          <l> veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
          <l> mutalaip pōttu muḻumī ṉārun</l>
          <l> taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ ṟērem</l>
          <l> muṉkaṭai niṟka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          'Long live Ātan! Long live Aviṉi!</l>
<l>          May there be no hunger! May sickness go far away!'</l>
<l>          That's what our mother wants. As for us:</l>
<l>          'May the chariot of the man from the village by the cool ghat</l>
<l>          where male crocodiles gorge on whole fish</l>
<l>          stop in front of our gate!' — that's what we want.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
